tory is made at the AFC Women's Asian Cup."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Piala Asia Wanita AFC Australia 2026 mempertemukan 12 tim terbaik di Asia.\n\nDiselenggarakan di 5 stadion kelas dunia di Perth, Gold Coast, dan Sydney, ini adalah perayaan sepak bola wanita terbesar di Asia.\n\nTampilkan sejarah di Piala Asia Wanita AFC."},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Der AFC Frauen-Asien-Pokal Australien 2026 bringt die zwölf besten Teams Asiens zusammen.\n\nIn fünf Weltklasse-Stadien in Perth, Gold Coast und Sydney ist dies Asiens größtes Frauenfußball-Fest.\n\nSeien Sie dabei, wenn beim AFC Frauen-Asien-Pokal Geschichte geschrieben wird."},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"La Copa Asiática Femenina de la AFC Australia 2026 reúne a los 12 mejores equipos de Asia.\n\nOrganizada en 5 estadios de clase mundial en Perth, Gold Coast y Sídney, esta es la mayor celebración del fútbol femenino en Asia.\n\nVive la historia de la Copa Asiática Femenina de la AFC."},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"AFC女子アジアカップ オーストラリア2026には、アジアのトップ12チームが集結します。\n\nパース、ゴールドコースト、シドニーの5つのワールドクラスのスタジアムで開催されるこの大会は、アジア最大の女子サッカーの祭典です。\n\nAFC女子アジアカップで歴史が作られる瞬間を、ぜひその場で体験してください。"},{"marketVariantId":"Korean","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"2026 AFC 여자 아시안컵 호주 대회에는 아시아 최고의 12개 팀이 참가합니다.\n\n퍼스 골드코스트 시드니의 세계적인 경기장 5곳에서 개최되는 이 대회는 아시아 최대 규모의 여자 축구 축제입니다.\n\nAFC 여자 아시안컵에서 역사가 만들어지는 순간을 함께하세요."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"La Coupe d'Asie féminine de l'AFC, Australie 2026, réunit les 12 meilleures équipes d'Asie.\n\nOrganisée dans 5 stades de renommée mondiale à Perth, Gold Coast et Sydney, c'est la plus grande célébration du football féminin en Asie.\n\nSoyez présent pour voir l'histoire s'écrire lors de la Coupe d'Asie féminine de l'AFC."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"A Copa Asiática Feminina da AFC Austrália 2026 reúne as 12 melhores seleções da Ásia.\n\nSediada em 5 estádios de classe mundial em Perth, Gold Coast e Sydney, esta é a maior celebração do futebol feminino na Ásia.\n\nEsteja presente quando a história for feita na Copa Asiática Feminina da AFC."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"2026年澳大利亚亚足联女足亚洲杯将汇聚亚洲12支顶尖球队。\n\n这项赛事将在珀斯、黄金海岸和悉尼的五座世界级体育场举行，是亚洲规模最大的女子足球盛会。\n\n见证亚足联女足亚洲杯创造历史的时刻。"},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"2026年澳洲亞足聯女足亞洲盃將匯集亞洲12支頂尖球隊。\n\n這項賽事將在珀斯、黃金海岸和雪梨的五座世界級體育場舉行，是亞洲規模最大的女子足球盛會。\n\n見證亞足聯女足亞洲盃創造歷史的時刻。"},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"L'AFC Women's Asian Cup Australia 2026 riunisce le 12 migliori squadre asiatiche.\n\nOspitata in 5 stadi di fama mondiale a Perth, Gold Coast e Sydney, questa è la più grande celebrazione del calcio femminile in Asia.\n\nSiate presenti quando si scrive la storia all'AFC Women's Asian Cup."}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"Gold Coast Stadium","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"Centreline Place","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Robina","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4226","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-28.0690131","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.3785456","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[],"internationalReach":"","rates":[],"deals":[],"jobVacancies":[],"weat