tCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"KOREAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Korean","commentText":"부드럽고 감미로운 보컬과 클래식 소울 그리고 현대적인 소울이 조화롭게 어우러진 젤렌 응온다가 2025년 초 전석 매진을 기록한 데 이어 2026년 호주 단독 콘서트 투어를 위해 돌아옵니다. \"If You Don't Want My Love\"라는 히트곡으로 널리 알려진 젤렌은 R&B 신의 최전선에 서 있으며 자신의 음악 스타일을 \"비치 보이스와 비틀즈의 감성이 가미된 모던 소울\"이라고 설명합니다."},{"marketVariantId":"Indonesian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"INDONESIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Indonesian","commentText":"Vokal yang halus dan lembut berpadu dengan perpaduan soul klasik dan kontemporer. Jalen Ngonda kembali untuk tur utama di Australia pada tahun 2026, setelah tiket terjual habis pada awal tahun 2025. Terkenal dengan lagunya yang langsung dikenali \"If You Don't Want My Love\", Jalen telah naik ke garis depan kancah R&B, menggambarkan gaya musiknya sendiri sebagai \"soul modern dengan sentuhan Beach Boys dan Beatles\"."},{"marketVariantId":"French","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"FRENCH","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"French","commentText":"Une voix suave et envoûtante se mêle à une soul classique et contemporaine. Jalen Ngonda revient en Australie pour une tournée de concerts en tête d'affiche en 2026, suite au succès retentissant de ses concerts début 2025. Célèbre pour son tube « If You Don't Want My Love », Jalen s'est imposé comme une figure incontournable de la scène R&B, décrivant son style comme « une soul moderne avec une touche des Beach Boys et des Beatles »."},{"marketVariantId":"Portuguese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"PORT-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Portuguese","commentText":"Vozes suaves e aveludadas se encontram com uma mistura de soul clássico e contemporâneo. Jalen Ngonda retorna para shows como atração principal na Austrália em 2026, após o sucesso de sua turnê no início de 2025, com ingressos esgotados. Mais conhecido por seu sucesso instantâneo \"If You Don't Want My Love\", Jalen ascendeu ao topo da cena R&B, descrevendo seu próprio som como \"soul moderno com um toque dos Beach Boys e dos Beatles\"."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Simplified","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-S","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Simplified","commentText":"丝滑柔顺的嗓音融合了经典与现代灵魂乐的精髓。继2025年初澳大利亚巡演门票售罄之后，Jalen Ngonda将于2026年重返澳大利亚，举办多场领衔演唱会。Jalen以其脍炙人口的歌曲《If You Don't Want My Love》而闻名，并已跻身R&B乐坛的领军人物之列。他将自己的音乐风格描述为“融合了海滩男孩和披头士乐队元素的现代灵魂乐”。"},{"marketVariantId":"German","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"GERMAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"German","commentText":"Samtig-weiche Stimme trifft auf eine Mischung aus klassischem und modernem Soul. Jalen Ngonda kehrt 2026 für eigene Headliner-Konzerte nach dem ausverkauften Erfolg Anfang 2025 zurück. Bekannt geworden durch seinen Ohrwurm „If You Don't Want My Love“, hat sich Jalen an die Spitze der R&B-Szene gespielt und beschreibt seinen eigenen Sound als „modernen Soul mit einem Hauch von Beach Boys und Beatles“."},{"marketVariantId":"Spanish","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"SPAN-EUR","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Spanish","commentText":"Una voz suave y sedosa se fusiona con una mezcla de soul clásico y contemporáneo. Jalen Ngonda regresa como cabeza de cartel en Australia en 2026, tras agotar las entradas a principios de 2025. Conocido por su reconocible tema \"If You Don't Want My Love\", Jalen se ha convertido en un referente de la escena R&B, describiendo su propio sonido como \"soul moderno con un toque de los Beach Boys y los Beatles\"."},{"marketVariantId":"Chinese Traditional","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"CHINESE-T","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Chinese Traditional","commentText":"絲滑柔順的嗓音融合了經典與現代靈魂樂的精髓。繼2025年初澳大利亞巡演門票售罄之後，Jalen Ngonda將於2026年重返澳大利亞，並舉辦多場領銜演唱會。 Jalen以其膾炙人口的歌曲《If You Don't Want My Love》而聞名，並已躋身R&B樂壇的領導者之列。他將自己的音樂風格描述為「融合了海灘男孩和披頭四元素的現代靈魂樂」。"},{"marketVariantId":"Japanese","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"JAPANESE","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Japanese","commentText":"シルキーで滑らかなボーカルと、クラシックソウルとコンテンポラリーソウルが融合。2025年初頭の完売を受け、ジャレン・ンゴンダが2026年のオーストラリア公演でヘッドライナーを務めることが決定。誰もが知る名曲「If You Don't Want My Love」で知られるジャレンは、R&Bシーンの最前線に躍り出ており、自身のサウンドを「ビーチ・ボーイズとビートルズのエッセンスを加えたモダンソウル」と表現している。"},{"marketVariantId":"Italian","attributeIdProductComment":"PRODTRANS ","attributeIdProductCommentDescription":"Product Description Translation","sequenceNumber":"100","attributeIdLanguageWritten":"ITALIAN","attributeIdLanguageWrittenDescription":"Italian","commentText":"Una voce vellutata incontra un mix di soul classico e contemporaneo. Jalen Ngonda torna in Australia per le date da headliner del 2026, dopo il tutto esaurito registrato all'inizio del 2025. Noto soprattutto per il suo brano immediatamente riconoscibile \"If You Don't Want My Love\", Jalen si è imposto sulla scena R&B, descrivendo il suo sound come \"soul moderno con un tocco dei Beach Boys e dei Beatles\"."}],"productSite":[{"siteName":"The Tivoli","attributeIdSiteType":"VENUE","attributeIdSiteTypeDescription":"Venue","productSiteAddressRelationship":[{"attributeIdAddress":"PHYSICAL","attributeIdAddressDescription":"Physical","addressLine1":"52 Costin Street","addressLine2":"","suburbName":"","cityName":"Fortitude Valley","areaName":"","stateName":"Queensland","countryName":"Australia","addressPostalCode":"4006","overrideDomesticRegionFlag":"0","geocodeGdaLatitude":"-27.4522597","geocodeGdaLongitude":"153.0314537","productSiteAddressStreetDirectoryRelationship":""}],"productSiteAttributeRelationship":"","productSiteCommentRelationship":"","productSiteCommunicationRelationship":"","productSiteLicenceRelationship":"","productSiteRelatedSiteRelationship":"","productSiteMultimediaRelationship":"","productSiteContactRelationship":""}],"mediaLinks":[],"alternateNames":[{"name":"The Tivoli","kind":""}],"internationalReach":"","rates":[{"ratesType":"ALLTICKETS","ratesTypeDescription":"All tickets","priceFrom":"89.90","priceTo":"89.90","free":"","rateComment":"Over 18 Years Only"}],"deals":[],"jobVacancies":[],"weather":"","menuUrl":"","winelistUrl":"","doesServeMeal":"","openingTime":{"openingTimeType":"","seasonalPeriods":[],"openingTimeComment":"","exceptions":{"exceptionPeriod":"","periods":[]}},"productProximity":[],"productWidget":[],"services":[],"verticalClassifications":[{"productTypeId":"PERFORMANC","productTypeDescription":"Concert or Performance"}],"pageURL":"/au/en/things-to-do/events/p-6965d0d03f1e2a9215972efc-jalen-ngonda","classificationLayer":[{"attributeId":"music-and-festivals"}]}}]},"disabledClassifications":["classes-and-workshops","participation-and-endurance","markets-and-community","business-event","food-and-wine"]}